########## shedule_at_hero ##########
Options
  debug.
  


Syntax
  l = l.

Verb l
  Does
    Look.
End Verb.


The loc1 Isa location
  
  Description
    "E to Loc2."
  
  Exit e To loc2.
  
End The loc1.

The loc2 Isa location
  
  Description
    "E to Loc1."
  
  Exit e To loc1.
  
End The loc2.
Event hello
  "Someone says: 'Hello!'."
  Schedule hello At hero After 2.
End Event hello.


Start At loc1.
  "A 'Hello' is scheduled at hero every other turn."
  Schedule hello At hero After 2.
  
